    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Material comprising the hollow, sharp spines of a porcupine, echidna, or hedgehog. Used in Native American ornamental embroidery and other decorative purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
